scripts.ci-test: eslint ./src && gulp pretest && cross-env NODE_PATH=./lib istanbul cover --report lcovonly --dir reports/coverage _mocha tests/lib/ -- --recursive --reporter dot
scripts.cover: gulp pretest && cross-env NODE_PATH=./lib istanbul cover --dir reports/coverage _mocha tests/lib/ -- --recursive -R progress
scripts.debug: cross-env NODE_PATH=./lib mocha debug --recursive --reporter dot tests/lib/
scripts.test: cross-env BABEL_ENV=test NODE_PATH=./src nyc -s mocha -R dot --recursive tests/src -t 5s
scripts.test-all: npm test && for resolver in ./resolvers/*; do cd $resolver && npm test && cd ../..; done
scripts.test-compiled: npm run prepublish && NODE_PATH=./lib mocha --compilers js:babel-register --recursive tests/src
